Quick and dirty microservice to kill and restart a particular server instance (hardcoded)

Set up instance using credentials through `aws configure` then run using:

`env FLASK_APP=microservice.py python3 -m flask run`

Sample restart URL: http://18.221.217.91:5000/restart?id=i-0f5850678bbd27ba0&region=us-east-2&force=true